      <title>马来西亚公司在特朗普关税后提出针对新税收的案件</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/malaysian-firms-make-case-against-new-taxes-post-trump-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[马来西亚制造商敦促政府避免在美国宣布向东南亚国家宣布24％的互惠关税后，今年不再引入额外的税收负担，理由是成本压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/malaysian-firms-make-case-against-new-taxes-post-trump-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Apr 2025 01:35:08 GMT</pubDate>
