    <item>
      <title>美国关税冲击激发记录中的销售后，黄金稳定</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/gold-steadies-after-us-tariff-shock-sparks-selloff-from-record</link>
      <description><![CDATA[黄金从其最新纪录的最新成绩跌落后稳定，珍贵的金属席卷了悲观的情绪，在美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）更具侵略性的关税议程之后，这一情绪席卷了全球市场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/gold-steadies-after-us-tariff-shock-sparks-selloff-from-record</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Apr 2025 00:05:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>经济学家说，亚洲首当其冲需要放松。</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/asia-bears-brunt-of-trump-tariffs-needs-to-ease-economists-say</link>
      <description><![CDATA[经济学家认为，亚洲的首当其冲，这将通过较弱的商业投资和情感来拖延区域增长，要求中央银行介入更多的利率削减。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/asia-bears-brunt-of-trump-tariffs-needs-to-ease-economists-say</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Apr 2025 00:04:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>家乐福筹集的提议要私有巴西杂货单位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/carrefour-raises-offer-to-take-brazilian-grocery-unit-private</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在重大投票前几天，随着少数股东动员起初的竞标，Carrefour SA就提出了将其巴西单位私人私有的提议。]]></description>
